title: Amiga music: AceMan - Robotized (Remix) (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
description:
"Robotized (Remix)" (2022) by AceMan (Jakub Szelag), original "Robotized" by JazzCat (won Decrunch 2022).
Art "Connecting" by Bifrost/Loonies, 4th at The Party 1999.

Original "Robotized" can be heard here (not the greatest quality upload):
https://youtu.be/tHqe7EToqGQ?t=382

There's also JazzCat's (Piotr Pacyna) studio track "Mechanics Of Funk", here:
https://www.neosounds.com/royalty-free-music/songs/20833/mechanics-of-funk-lynnemusic

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio.

Visit my channel for more Amiga music.
